                                                    de la imagen</label>
                                                <input type="text" id="alternative" name="alternative"
                                                    class="block w-full p-4 text-gray-900 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 sm:text-md focus:ring-marronBg focus:border-marronBg"
